This Project demonstrates a Hand Gestures Controlled Car that uses Computer Vision that is Mediapipe to Recognize hand gestures and WIFI Communication to send command to ESP32 which drives the car.
Concept!!!
The Computers Webcam captures the live video
The Mediapipe library using hand landmark detects the hand Gestures
The python script sends to the ESP32 via WIFI
The ESP32 as as the AP which recievs the command and drives BO MOTORS using L298N Motor Driver
